      "description": "CreateProductRequest is the request for creating a new product.\n\nv1.3 note (PRD §0.1 D4): if product_type_id is supplied, the server will\nauto-generate product_code via the CodeGenerator (CST{TYPE}{YY}{MM}{SEQ:6})\nand any client-supplied product_code is ignored. If product_type_id is\nempty, product_code must be supplied manually (legacy Phase 1 path)."
